---
title: Perfect Penne Bake with Chicken Sausage and Kale
description: When we say this pasta recipe is perfect, we really mean it. It’s got all the gooey deliciousness of lasagna with none of the hassle or tedious layering. Featuring tender kale, meaty chicken sausage, a healthy sprinkle of cheese, and penne cooked until it’s just al dente, everything about it is a pasta-lover’s fantasy.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/baked-penne-with-chicken-sausage-d986fb6c.jpg
